quran[18]{c,v,t,f}:
  37,127,"Basi ŵankaaniile, basi chisimu ŵanganyao tachiika nao (ku ilagasyo)."
  37,128,"Ikaŵeje achikapolo ŵa Allah ŵakuswejesyedwa."
  37,129,"Ni twannechele (mbili syambone) kwa (ŵandu wosope) ŵakwika munyuma."
  40,70,"Aŵala ŵaachikaaniile Chitabu (cha Qur’an), ni ayila yatwaatumiisye nayo Achimitenga Ŵetu (ya chikulupi cha Tauhidi ni yakwimuka m’malembe). Basi tachiika kumanyilila (ipotesi yakanila kwao)."
  40,71,"Ndema jagachiŵa makongwa mu ngosi mwao, kwisa soni unyolo (mu ngongolo mwao) ali nkuwutidwa."
  40,72,"M’mesi gamasemule kusyene, kaneko tachiŵa nkuchomedwa m’Moto."
  41,49,"Mundu (kafili) jwangapela kuŵenda yambone (kwa Allah, Allah ni akumpaga nambo jwangatogolela), sano naga inkwayiye yakusakala basi jukasaŵa jwakwasa ntima, jwakata tama."
  41,50,"Soni chisimu naga tuli tumpele kupasya ukoto wakuuma Kukwetu panyuma pa masausyo gagankwayiye, chisimu akasaŵechetaga kuti: “Ayi niyangune (ni jwaanguŵajilwa kupata yeleyi ligongo lyaumanyilisi wangu), soni nganguganichisya yanti Kiyama kuŵa nkwiima. Nambo naga timbuchisyidwe kwa Ambuje ŵangu, nikuti chisimu une tinjipata yambone Kukwakwe.” Basi tuchatagulila kwene aŵala ŵaakufuulu yaŵapanganyisye, ni chitukape kupasya kwene mu ilagasyo yakandapala."
  41,51,"Soni naga tuli tumpele ukoto mundu, jukasanyosyaga ni galauchila kumbali, nambo naga inkwayiye yakusakala, basi jukasaŵa ni maduwa gamalewulewu."
  42,34,"Kapena kuijonanga (yomboyo nikwamisya achinsyeneo) ligongo lya (yangalumbana) yapanganyisye, ni jukuisimasyaga yaijinji."
  42,35,"Ni akumanyilila aŵala ŵaakukangana pa ma Ȃya Getu (yanti): Nganakola ŵanganyao kwakutilila."
  42,36,"Sano chindu chilichose chim’bele nkupedwa, basi chigambile kuŵa chisengwasyo (channono) cha umi wa duniya, nambo yaili kwa Allah ni yambone nnope soni yakwendelechela kwa aŵala ŵaakulupilile, soni kwa M’mbuje gwao pe (Allah) akwegamilaga."
  43,16,"Kapena (Allah) alitendele ŵanache ŵachikongwe mu yaagumbile, sano jenumanja ni ansagulile ŵanache ŵachilume?"
  43,17,"Soni naga jumo jwao juli jupedwile abali ja ayila yannandanyichisye (Allah) Jwaukoto wejinji (yakola mwanache jwankongwe), basi ngope jakwe jikasapiilila, soni gakasan’gumbala madandausi."
  43,18,"Ha! Ana jwaaleledwe mu ipeto, soni jwalakwe pa ukangani nganijuŵa juŵechete mwakupikanika (ni jwankumpa Allah, ŵali ŵanache ŵachikongwe)?"
  44,1,"Hâ. Mîm. ",1:[Asi harufusi ni chimpepe mu isimosimo ya Qur’an. Ni pangali jwine jwaakumanyilila mate gakwe ikaŵeje Allah pe basi.]
  44,2,"Nguchilumbila Chitabu (cha Qur’an) chakusalichisya."
  44,3,"Chisimu Uwwe tujitulwisye jalakwe (Qur’an) m’Chilo Chaupile, chisimu Uwwe tuŵele Akutetela."